Premium Typography & Spacing"
Goal: Refine the visual hierarchy and readability

Tasks:
Task 1: Custom Font Integration

Add premium fonts:
- Heading font: "Bebas Neue" or "Oswald" (industrial, bold)
- Body font: "Inter" or "DM Sans" (clean, readable)
- Install via next/font/google
- Update tailwind.config.ts
- Apply throughout site

Task 2: Typography System

Create lib/typography.ts:
- Consistent heading sizes (h1-h6)
- Body text variants (large, base, small)
- Use CSS variables or Tailwind classes
- Document the system in comments

Task 3: Spacing Refinement

Audit and fix spacing:
- Consistent section padding (py-24, py-32)
- Proper content max-width (max-w-7xl)
- Better component spacing
- Visual rhythm between sections

Task 4: Micro-copy Polish

Review and improve all text:
- Headlines more compelling
- CTAs more action-oriented
- Descriptions more engaging
- Add subtle taglines/quotes
